&nbsp;

<a href="http://www.fubiz.net/2013/05/07/what-the-world-eats/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-16481 size-medium" src="http://localhost:9090/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/eat2-450x297.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="297" /></a> <strong>VS.</strong> <img class="alignnone wp-image-16482 size-medium" src="http://localhost:9090/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/eat1-450x297.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="297" />

&nbsp;

מה אוכלים לארוחת בוקר מסביב לעולם?[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="right" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_video link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ry1E1uzPSU0" align="center"][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="right" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]סדרה מרתקת של הנשיונל ג'אוגרפיק בת 10 פרקים על "טביעת רגל אקולוגית":[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="right" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_video link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VcxQjGPDKHE&amp;list=PLfEPWuMR8I9ctnB1VmkDPaltRpWjfkkfT" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
